answer: The main Novartis financial results page is `investors.novartis.com/investors/financial-data/quarterly-results`. Under this, individual quarterly reports (e.g., Q3 2024 released Oct 29, 2024, Q4 2024 released Jan 31, 2025) and condensed financial reports are available, always including the release date and quarter.
